                            <comment id="174084" author="jay" created="Thu, 17 Nov 2016 17:06:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Do we really need to handle LOOKUP_REVAL in ll_revalidate_dentry() as dentries in LLITE is protected by a lock?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
